## ğŸªª 5. Certificate Workflow

1. User completes all module quizzes â†’ average score â‰¥ 50%.  
2. Supabase function generates PDF using user name & completion date.  
3. Store file in `certificates/{userId}.pdf` in Supabase Storage.  
4. Email user with download link (automated).  
5. Certificate visible on dashboard (card state = Completed).  

